<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to MediTrack</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #3b82f6;
        }
        p {
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to MediTrack, <%= username %>!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for registering. We are thrilled to have you on board.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
        <p>Best Regards,<br>The MediTrack Team</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MediTrack. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
